ing holding companies in public utility field but up to now no one believed the President was looking into other fields His statement was greeted with both wonder and amazement in finan cial circles which pointed out that about half of all the wkitly held listed securities represent concerns which"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-01-27T16:58:35.545Z", "group": ["ndnp/fu", "university-of-florida-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83016244/1938-01-31/ed-1/?sp=3", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_cicerone_ver01:data:sn83016244:00271761314:1938013101:0129/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=266&w=216", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_cicerone_ver01:data:sn83016244:00271761314:1938013101:0129/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=533&w=433", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_cicerone_ver01:data:sn83016244:00271761314:1938013101:0129/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1066&w=866", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/fu/batch_fu_cicerone_ver01/data/sn83016244/00271761314/1938013101/0129.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["monroe county", "monroe", "florida", "key west", "united states"], "location_city": ["key west"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["monroe"], "location_state": ["florida"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["2", "sn83016244", "0", "3", "6", "7", "0000000003", "1", "4"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn83016244"], "number_page": ["0000000003"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "2", "7", "1", "7", "6", "1", "3", "1", "4"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the key west citizen (ke